I felt a church mothers anointing creep up on me….you remember  the mothers that use to be at the altar saying JESUS in your ear!!!!!! Whew 🔥🔥🔥🔥 

That thing hit me so hard! I’m glad my wig didn’t come off 🤣😂😂😂😂😂😂

Why do we gather if Jesus is not the center? Why do we come here if he’s not the center? Why do we sing and tell of the good news if he’s not the center of it all!!!!! We are HERE for not other! I’m ready to see more miracles, signs and wonders happening through believers!!!!! If you haven’t downloaded my little brother @thethirdmelvincrispell album “No Failure” you need to do so ASAP! From start to finish is amazing. So glad I got the chance to celebrate with him at his album release party this past Saturday night in Charlotte, NC! I love you Melvin always and forever. Keep your pure heart, it’ll continue to take you places and even further than what you would ever be able to imagine.
